marinac@touchedbycancer.org\">email Susan Marinac</a> or call 216 455-1512\r\n</p><p>\r\n	To participate in Group for Those with Cancer in Beachwood \r\n	<a href=\"mailto:mailto:kohn@touchedbycancer.org\">email Betsy Kohn</a> or call 216 455-1508\r\n</p><p>\r\n	To participate in Group for Those with Cancer in Westlake email \r\n	<a href=\"mailto:mailto:heyman@touchedbycancer.org\">Ellen Heyman</a> or call 216 455-1507<br>\r\n</p><p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-10 11:12:08','2015-06-10 11:14:42','b6e91135-2b15-4113-b5c5-3fb0567b41dd'),(225,301,'en_us','Cancer Specific Programs',NULL,'<p>\r\n	Our cancer specific programs include drop-in groups where those facing cancer can gain information, gather for support, and share their concerns. Family members are welcome.\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<p>\r\n	Registration is not required for cancer specific groups.\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-10 11:19:23','2015-06-10 11:30:27','abd7f635-9feb-4d24-900f-037c4575bee7'),(226,302,'en_us','Breast Cancer Programs',NULL,'<p>\r\n	We offer a support group for young women with breast cancer that meets on the 2nd Tuesday of each month. This monthly group is for women in their 20s, 30s and 40s and meets at our Westlake location from 6:30-8:00pm. For more information about this group \r\n	<a href=\"mailto:marinac@touchedbycancer.org\">email Susan Marinac, LISW-S</a> or call 216 455-1512.\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<p>\r\n	Other programs at The Gathering Place that you may want to consider include our yoga and tai chi which can be good for relaxation and gentle stretching, our exercise classes which help to manage the physical side effects of cancer treatment or one-to-one counseling to help cope with the emotional impact of a cancer diagnosis.\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>\r\n	If you are interested in talking with a program staff member contact Mary Fisher Bornstein in Beachwood or Susan Marinac in Westlake\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-10 11:43:44','2015-06-10 12:15:24','cfad0398-d77f-476b-bd8b-6bf9af5456f8'),(227,305,'en_us','Prostate Cancer Programs',NULL,'<p>The Gathering Place offers various educational, support and exercise programs to support men with prostate cancer including Prostate Partners which is a monthly group. Family members are welcome to attend Prostate Partners which meets on the 2nd Tuesday of every month in Beachwood from 6:30-8:00pm and the 3rd Tuesday of every month in Westlake from 6:30-8:00pm. There is no registration required for Prostate Partners.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-10 11:55:47','2015-06-10 11:55:47','105d8f7e-31f8-4e8f-a08e-c5ad3f3f5476'),(228,306,'en_us','Cancer Survivorship Programs',NULL,'<p>Our cancer survivorship programs are ....</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'For individuals who have completed cancer treatment.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>For more information about our survivorship programs contact Betsy Kohn in Beachwood or Susan Marinac in Westlake.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-10 11:59:38','2015-06-10 11:59:38','b8d834dd-b543-4840-a3fc-77bcf244a37b'),(229,309,'en_us','Young Adults with Cancer',NULL,'<p>\r\n	These programs are designed to help cope with the unique needs that come with being diagnosed with cancer as a young