u have a personal or family history of any of these cancers, have been diagnosed with a BRCA mutations, or are considering genetic testing, this is a great opportunity to connect with others in similar situations. Enjoy light refreshments and a tour of The Gathering Place and its gardens.</p><p><strong>Advance registration required.</strong></p><p>TGP East: Tuesday, August 4th, 6:30-8:00pm<br></p>','2015-08-04 18:30:00',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-14 00:07:56','2015-06-14 00:07:56','21b10d47-e483-4f8d-aa68-238a6047ad4d'),(320,458,'en_us','If Cancer is a Gift, Where is the Returns Counter? (O)',NULL,'<p>Mindy Greenstein, PhD explores the balancing act of coping with cancer, based on her personal and professional experience. Dr. Greenstein is a cancer psychologist and consultant to the psychiatry department at Memorial Sloan-Kettering Cancer Center, as well as a two-time breast cancer survivor. Dessert reception follows program. </p><p><strong>Advance registration required.</strong></p><p>Corporate College East, 4400 Richmond Rd, Warrensville Heights: Thursday, September 10th, 7:30-8:30pm<br></p>','2015-09-10 19:30:00',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-14 00:13:58','2015-06-14 00:13:58','5196807c-40c1-4db5-a694-f772fd194387'),(321,460,'en_us','Applying the Principles of Meaning Centered Therapy to your Practice and your Life (O)',NULL,'<p>Professionals will learn the basic principles of meaning centered therapy and explore how these principles help individuals facing cancer find a sense of meaning and how they can be applied to the professional\'s own life and work. 1 CEU provided for social workers, counselors, marriage and family therapists, and psychologists. Continental breakfast 8:00-8:30am followed by program 8:30-9:30am.</p><p>Presenter: Mindy Greenstein, PhD</p><p><strong>Advance registration required.</strong></p><p>Cuyahoga Community College East, 4250 Richmond Road, Warrensville Heights: Friday, September 11th, 8:00-9:30am<br></p>','2015-09-11 08:00:00',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-14 00:22:03','2015-06-14 00:22:03','0f8afe24-c0d7-4cfe-8484-6e855b47d1f4'),(322,462,'en_us','Guided Meditation (E)',NULL,'<p>Relax, learn new coping skills and practice mindfulness meditation techniques in a group setting.</p><p>Facilitator: Eileen Coan, MA, MLS</p><p>TGP East: Mondays, July 6th &amp; 20th, August 3rd &amp; 17th &amp; September 21st, 2:00-2:45pm<br></p>','2015-07-06 14:00:00',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Eileen Coan</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-14 00:28:55','2015-06-14 00:28:55','35c75627-fa0c-41e6-9b1f-0f627fb9f56b'),(323,464,'en_us','Guided Meditation (W)',NULL,'<p>Relax, learn new coping skills and practice mindfulness meditation techniques in a group setting.</p><p>Facilitator: Erin Rafter, PhD, CCLS</p><p>TGP West: Mondays, July 13th &amp; 27th, August 10th &amp; 24th &amp; September 14th &amp; 28th, 5:30-6:15pm<br></p>','2015-07-13 17:30:00',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Erin Rafter</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-06-14 00:34:45','2015-06-14 00:34:45','9e7137a8-8000-4e69-823e-90ef132e1e39'),(324,466,'en_us','Charity Navigator','<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed nec sem in lacus mat